Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE PERIL OF\NTHE GREAT PURIFICATION SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}G-Gods!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it wouldn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense a tremendous number of monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you... If you just\Nrelax and try again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My Insignia of Aban won't glow\Nno matter how much I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried time and time again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's never glowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,About the Insignias\Nand the power of our souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You all did it just by thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't even get mine to flicker!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I trained desperately,\Nbut nothing changed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I took this last make-or-break shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but it still didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all... It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But my strength\Njust isn't enough for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you give this to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,someone as inept as me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, even if Leona casts\NMinakator, it won't be strong enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're completely surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen these monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I not sense all these monsters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they were in those Magic Capsules.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They set a trap for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold! The elite warriors\Nof the New Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all monsters from the Underworld,\Nthe home of us Darklings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?!\N-The Underworld?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters of the Underworld are far more\Npowerful than Surface World monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You pieces of filth\Ndon't stand a chance against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll make quick work of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Even with Crocodine,\Nthere's so many...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You must complete Minakator!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you move from there, the power\Nof the four of you will vanish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the fighting to us!\NYou just need one more to complete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Queen Flora! I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, Aban would never choose\Nthe wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We'll handle the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way you can handle them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we can't move, our forces...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine, how many can you handle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They may be unknown, powerful monsters,\Nbut I can take 40 or 50 of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai and the others\Nhave to focus on Minakator!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hold off the enemy ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said, Hero of the North!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As former head of the Furfang Legion\NI should be able to handle about 100!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you relax!\NSo what if they're from the Underworld?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Show them the Beast King Commando spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.88,On Top,,0,0,0,,EVERYONE THINKS,\N"CAPTAIN IS AMAZING!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ursula, Drohly, Nibbles,\Nhold off the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Terry, Drack-Drack, Rumbles,\Nattack from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Otoad, Spikey, Seari,\Nrun around to cause confusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan, you're the messenger!\NTell Dai and the others to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Mr. Beast is right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at his bravery!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, follow Mr. Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! Don't try to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is hold them off\Nwhile the Princess completes her spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you the same thing\Nyou once said to me, Ron Berku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as the two of us are tied up here,\Nyou have no hope of victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The tables have turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell is taking so long?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, everyone is trying to hold\Nthe monster army at bay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! You have to try again! Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, let's make a tactical retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how long I try here,\NI don't think it'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We've rescued Hyunckel. If we retreat now\Nand try again when we're ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, I told you.\NThere's no second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Having come this far, our enemy will never\Nlet us approach Ban Palace again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our last chance to cast Minakator.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, if you run now,\Nyour Insignia will never glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The soul's power makes Kiseiseki glow.\NThere's no difficult technique to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:10:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is inside of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you choose to run now,\Nyour soul will have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Insignia will never glow\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?! Why can't Popp do it?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has such a kind and honorable soul!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just give this thing\Nto somebody else!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not... I'm not like any of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not royalty\Nor any kind of born warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.63,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}MEDOROA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:59.63,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}DARK INCENSE{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage, Fortitude, Justice, Love...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What else is there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A power unique to my soul?\NDo I really have that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, tell me what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's some way to do this\NI'll do whatever it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you guys have the answer then tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bear to see anyone die for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We all will die anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with all the people\Nof the Surface World.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear your mind, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was once steeped in evil,\Nand yet my Insignia now glows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You've pursued justice.\NThere's no way you'll fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You gave me\Nthe final bit of courage I needed, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:12:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how strong your soul is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter the odds, you've always stood\Nstrong. I admire you more than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want admiration from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those five...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They must be forming up for\Nsome kind of spell of light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One isn't glowing. It's that Mage brat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can put a stop to that spell\Nwhile crushing the remaining human forces,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it will be an even greater\Ncontribution to King Ban!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I do that, no matter how much\Nthat Mystban despises me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}King Ban will accept me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish him with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A life falls for my bright future!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, fight with\Nyour hearts of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp, cast aside your doubt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are a true Disciple of Aban!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you always say such things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just expressing how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's because he's in love with you, Maam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, to be told what you feel for him\Nis just admiration...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:14:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is there... Is there anything I can do?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Any little thing for Popp in his plight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is there any way I can be useful to Popp?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this evil power?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?! Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A horrid mass\Nof malice and Dark Power...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This Venom Chain has been steeped\Nin my Dark Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,making it a bullet to pierce my enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even just a scratch on the body\Nis enough for its deadly poison to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not work on those four\Nbathed in holy light,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will be fatal to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Popp. This isn't the time to argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:15:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Popp!\NI don't believe that you can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You think too much of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If I run now, you won't have\Na reason to keep standing here, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have it in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't stand watching others\Nget hurt because of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If this makes you think\Nless of me, so be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, stop that projectile!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,M--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! That little girl got in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody! A Hoimi spell!\NShe needs a Hoimi spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,None of you must move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beyond help now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your Circle of Magic\Ngo to waste because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Popp will be the fifth star.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru, why?! Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This weapon was aimed at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't have to be a shield for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for someone worthless like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to die for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so thick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru believes in you more than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because she's in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you, Princess.\NI wanted to tell him myself someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No... That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt I'd ever be able to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, I've always loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,From the first time we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You always act like a clown,\Nbut you're so strong inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter your suffering,\Nyour fear, or your sadness...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you always, always overcome it in the end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For someone withdrawn like me,\Nyou are my inspiration.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed you so I could be near you,\Nbut I could never say how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so afraid that doing so\Nwould ruin what relationship we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I always hated how weak I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first time,\NI've been useful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! The wound's too deep\Nand she's been poisoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a Behoma spell couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just cast Hoimi on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you grant my last request?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the answer.\NIt's just a selfish request.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me who it is\Nthat you're in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And that it's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to hear you say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That way I can give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, when I'm reborn again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:20:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I can be someone\Nwith bravery like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Meruru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My Insignia of Aban! It's glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why is my Insignia...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it. The power of my soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was Courage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then it wasn't Dai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one with the soul of Courage was Popp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was just like Meruru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was afraid of ruining things\Nwith Maam and the others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru, look! My Insignia...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Meruru! Please! Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't die! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't die for someone like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp's a Mage,\Nand yet he's using healing energy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a Sage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:12.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:18.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:24.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:29.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:35.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:41.92,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:47.55,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:53.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:59.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:05.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:10.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:16.83,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:22.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:25.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:30.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to Meruru,\Nthe power of Popp's soul awakens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His Insignia of Aban glows with the color\Nof Courage, and the Pillar of Light rises.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.57,0:23:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Disciples of Aban\Nrestart the ritual to cast Minakator.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In Ban Palace, someone awaits them\Nthat not even Dark King Ban expected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:23:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.42,0:23:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Last Challenge"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.21,0:24:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.21,0:24:04.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,
